        <p>
          The platform transforms physical stadium space into digital assets by mapping field coordinates to blockchain NFTs. These tokenized sections create tradeable ownership across multiple sports, allowing fans to purchase NFTs representing specific grid coordinates on the playing field.
        </p>
        <p>
          Once ownership is established, the real magic begins. When gameplay action occurs in owned sections—goals, fouls, or other events—automated reward distributions trigger through smart contracts. Real-time blockchain tracking ensures immediate recognition of field events without delays or manual verification.
        </p>
        <p>
