        </p>
        <h3><strong>Real-Time Event Rewards</strong></h3>
        <p>
          Moving beyond passive collectibles, Fan Game Cube turns digital field sections into active participation tools. Fans who own NFT coordinates earn points when real game events happen at their exact locations, creating direct connections between physical match action and digital asset value.
        </p>
        <p>
          The reward mechanism operates autonomously. Events like goals or fouls trigger instant distributions to section owners through smart contract execution. This ensures transparent, immediate reward delivery without manual intervention or administrative overhead.
        </p>
        <p>
          As matches progress, the system continuously tracks events and updates reward distributions in real-time. Section ownership becomes a dynamic experience where every play matters, transforming how fans engage with the sports they love.
        </p>
        <h3><strong>Key Benefits and Advantages</strong></h3>
