            <li>Real-time tracking connecting physical gameplay to digital asset value</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <h3><strong>Revenue Sharing Model</strong></h3>
        <p>
          Building on these advantages, the platform establishes true revenue sharing between clubs and fans through tokenized field ownership. Primary NFT sales generate immediate revenue, while secondary trading creates ongoing engagement and sustained fan interest.
